headline: Housing Stocks Hit Hard by Gloomy Outlooks, Trump’s Snub
summary: The declines were led by Green Brick Partners Inc., Lennar Corp., Champion Homes Inc., Dream Finders Homes Inc., Installed Building Products Inc., DR Horton Inc. and TopBuild Corp. Mortgage-exposed companies like Rocket Cos Inc. fell as well.  Lowe’s forecast full-year sales that fell short of expectations, in a sign the housing market will remain lackluster in the near term, following close on the heels of cautionary comments from Home Depot Inc. that macroeconomic challenges remain.
